  "3089130": {
    "name": "时尚梦想家",
    "steam_appid": 3089130,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款第一人称模拟游戏，你将经营一家百货公司。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将你简陋的商店扩张为一家百货巨头。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/97f7577783f0c18dee9ec543fc519068.poster.avif?t=1768220481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/97f7577783f0c18dee9ec543fc519068.webm?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/97f7577783f0c18dee9ec543fc519068.mp4?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>合作模式和单人游戏</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在合作模式中与好友合作共赢（最多支持4 名玩家）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店中的玩家越多，光顾您商店的顾客就越多。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，您可以单独行动并管理商店中的一切。如果您改变主意，可以随时邀请您的朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/7d4341445af89d7879ce09664d6f6544.poster.avif?t=1768220481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/7d4341445af89d7879ce09664d6f6544.webm?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/7d4341445af89d7879ce09664d6f6544.mp4?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >商店流程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与头部品牌签订合同，用游戏内的电脑订购新产品，拆开包装，将产品放入你的商店，并为你的产品设定价格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在商店中设定产品价格时考虑市场价格，让客户满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >始终保持商店整洁，以免失去任何客户。此外，要小心小偷，别让产品丢失，不然会导致您的财务漏洞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/c8d924e632fecfe243ac4bab8caeafb4.poster.avif?t=1768220481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/c8d924e632fecfe243ac4bab8caeafb4.webm?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/c8d924e632fecfe243ac4bab8caeafb4.mp4?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >产品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请确保你的客户在商店中能找到他们想要的商品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断扩大你的产品数量让你的客户满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >衬衫、夹克、裤子、运动衫、连衣裙、T 恤、鞋子、帽子等等……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意市场价格并在价格便宜时购买更多产品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/ff25b7bda694ec627e9b011223aa40e5.poster.avif?t=1768220481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/ff25b7bda694ec627e9b011223aa40e5.webm?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/ff25b7bda694ec627e9b011223aa40e5.mp4?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >顾客</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设置足够数量的收银台和试衣间，减少顾客的等待时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扫描产品并收取现金或刷卡付款。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要忘记完成在线订单。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/7028fbc74ff25b09a45dc51929ed8098.poster.avif?t=1768220481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/7028fbc74ff25b09a45dc51929ed8098.webm?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/7028fbc74ff25b09a45dc51929ed8098.mp4?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩张和新员工</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过升级商店和提高预算来扩大你的商店和仓库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >雇佣库管来填满货架。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买更多收银机并雇佣新收银员，以尽量减少收银台的长队并减少顾客的等待时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/f7ec64dfed9fcac64d06aa907b8329a1.poster.avif?t=1768220481\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/f7ec64dfed9fcac64d06aa907b8329a1.webm?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089130/extras/f7ec64dfed9fcac64d06aa907b8329a1.mp4?t=1768220481\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
